data.name: Rider of the Storm Winds
data.desc: You can target 1 Dragon Normal Monster you control; equip this monster from your hand or field to that target. If a monster equipped with this card attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage to your opponent. If a monster equipped with this card would be destroyed, destroy this card instead.

card_sets.set_name: Saga of Blue-Eyes White Dragon Structure Deck
